snippet.title: Havoc Fox: Teaser Trailer [August 2019]
snippet.description:
It's time for our first trailer!
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Welcome to the world of Havoc Fox! The once peaceful continent of Vanalia has fallen victim to the tyrannic rule of its new ruler, and it's up to you to stop him! Do you have what it takes to save the continent?
----------------------------------------------------------
Try the demo! https://www.havocfoxgame.com/
Join our Discord: discord.gg/havoc-studios
----------------------------------------------------------
Trailer track 1 (Kingdom Requiem) composed by Nicole Frische.
Trailer track 2 composed by Leila "Woofle" Wilson.
